channel.description:
[center][b][size=24pt]A Ranking System[/size]
[size=14pt]Inspired by Call of Duty: Modern Warfare 2[/size][/b][/center]

Features:

[ul][li]Pk Points[/li]
[li]Killstreaks[/li]
[list]
[li]Most killed record[/li]
[/list]
[li]Experience[/li]
[li]Rank names[/li]
[li]Bonuses by killstreak[/li]
[li]No use of process[/li][/ul]


Bugs:

[ul][li]Says you have earned 0 bonus experience.[/li][/ul]


