You have now successfully allowed it to save and load the variables.

Now, you may notice errors. To fix them, open up Player (com.rs2.model.players) and add this somewhere:
[code=java]
	private RankingSystemConstants rSC = new RankingSystemConstants();

	public RankingSystemConstants getRankingConstants() {
		return rSC;
	}
[/code]
This simply allows us to call the class any time we want to from Client or Player.

